#. Tag: listitem
#: commands.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<simpara><action>Save the symbol being edited</action></simpara> <simpara>If "
"the symbol being edited was selected from the library, saving will update "
"that symbol. If it is a new symbol, it will be appended to the library and "
"subsequent saves will append another new symbol to the library. </simpara>"
msgstr ""
"<simpara><action>Sačuvajte simbol koji se uređuje</action></simpara> "
"<simpara> Ukoliko je uređivani simbol selektovan iz biblioteke, spašavanje "
"će ažurirati simbol.Ukoliko je novi simbol dodat će se u biblioteku i "
"kasnijim spašavanjem će se dodati još jedan novi simbol u biblioteku. </"
"simpara>"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: commands.docbook:39
#, no-c-format
msgid "Save Symbol as New"
msgstr "Spasi simbol kao novi"

#. Tag: listitem
#: commands.docbook:40
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<simpara><action>Save the symbol being edited as a new symbol</action></"
"simpara> <simpara>When a symbol is saved as new it will be appended to the "
"library regardless of it having originally been selected from the library "
"for editing. Subsequent saves will append another new symbol to the library. "
"</simpara>"
msgstr ""
"<simpara><action>Sačuvajte simbol koji se uređuje kao novi simbol</action></"
"simpara> <simpara>Kada je simbol spremljen kao novi on će se dodati u "
"biblioteku, bez obzira na to što je prvobitno bio selektovan  iz biblioteke "
"za uređivanje.Naknadno spašavanje će dodati još jedan novi simbol u "
"biblioteku.</simpara>"

